    <item>
      <title>传中国信托考虑退出台湾新光集团收购战</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-20/ctbc-is-said-to-consider-pulling-out-of-shin-kong-takeover-battle-in-taiwan</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，中国信托金融控股股份有限公司将决定不向新光金融控股股份有限公司提出新的收购要约，这将为竞争对手台新金融控股股份有限公司推进台湾金融业多年来最大的并购案之一铺平道路。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-20/ctbc-is-said-to-consider-pulling-out-of-shin-kong-takeover-battle-in-taiwan</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 20 Sep 2024 02:17:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>分析人士称，斯里兰卡的市场损失将因选举结果而进一步加剧</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-20/sri-lanka-s-market-losses-set-to-worsen-on-polls-analysts-say</link>
      <description><![CDATA[分析师表示，由于主要候选人承诺在选举后重新谈判条款，国际货币基金组织的贷款计划面临风险，斯里兰卡资产似乎将遭受更多损失。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-20/sri-lanka-s-market-losses-set-to-worsen-on-polls-analysts-say</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 20 Sep 2024 02:02:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国人民银行维持利率不变，各大银行维持基准贷款利率不变</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-20/china-s-banks-maintain-key-lending-rates-as-pboc-stays-on-pause</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于政策制定者推迟推出进一步的货币刺激措施，而金融机构正努力应对创纪录的低利润率，中国的各银行维持 9 月份基准贷款利率不变。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-20/china-s-banks-maintain-key-lending-rates-as-pboc-stays-on-pause</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 20 Sep 2024 01:01:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美团股价飙升 63% 面临中国消费疲软的风险</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-20/meituan-s-63-stock-surge-faces-risks-in-china-consumer-malaise</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美团专注于低价策略，帮助这家中国食品外卖公司在经济放缓拖累同行的情况下超额完成销售目标。投资者现在想知道，随着宏观经济疲软加剧，其股价的大幅上涨能否持续。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-20/meituan-s-63-stock-surge-faces-risks-in-china-consumer-malaise</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 20 Sep 2024 00:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>印度央行利用 6890 亿美元储备控制卢比汇率波动</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-19/india-s-das-tames-once-volatile-rupee-with-689-billion-reserves</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度央行行长沙克提坎塔·达斯（Shaktikanta Das）做出了一项罕见的平衡举措：抑制卢比波动，同时允许其走低以帮助总理纳伦德拉·莫迪实现出口目标。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-19/india-s-das-tames-once-volatile-rupee-with-689-billion-reserves</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 19 Sep 2024 23:51:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美联储降息后油价有望周线上涨，焦点为中东问题</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-19/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-september-20</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美联储大幅降息后，油价有望创下自四月份以来的最大单周涨幅，同时交易员继续关注中东地区不断升温的紧张局势。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-19/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-september-20</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 19 Sep 2024 23:31:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>全球股市延续涨势，日元在日本央行行动前上涨：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-19/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[亚洲股市延续全球股市的涨势，就业数据支持了美国经济将软着陆的观点。日本央行公布政策决定前，日元小幅走高。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-19/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 19 Sep 2024 22:38:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>印度禁止 Axis Bank 子公司管理新债发行</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-19/india-bars-axis-bank-unit-from-managing-new-debt-offerings</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度资本市场监管机构禁止 Axis Capital Ltd. 担任印度公司新债发行的管理人，这是该国证券市场的最新一次打击行动。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-19/india-bars-axis-bank-unit-from-managing-new-debt-offerings</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 19 Sep 2024 15:05:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>日本男孩被杀事件让习近平的民族主义面临反思</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-19/xi-s-nationalism-faces-reckoning-after-murder-of-japanese-boy</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在与对手关系紧张之际，国家主席习近平推动中国民族主义情绪高涨，以提高政府的支持率。现在，日本一名男孩被杀事件暴露了这种策略的危险性。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-19/xi-s-nationalism-faces-reckoning-after-murder-of-japanese-boy</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 19 Sep 2024 11:02:41 GMT</pubDate>
